    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STRAY CAT</h2> This is a small game about a homeless cat who decided to save money for a new home. 2D platformer with a side view, where you will play as a brave cat who decided to collect all the coins on his way and destroy evil opponents.<br><br><strong>In the game you will definitely have to:</strong><br>- Collect coins;<br>- Dodge sharp sawing discs and projectiles;<br>- Search for the key to the cave;<br>- Fight with enemies;<br>- Jump on trampolines;<br>- Climbing vines;<br>- Push crates;<br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br>- Suitable for children (The game is not very difficult and there is no blood in it);<br>- The game has original author's graphics;<br>- Pleasant soundtrack.",
